### Test Forgot Password Feature
### You can run these directly in VS Code with the REST Client extension
### Install: https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=humao.rest-client

### 1. Request Password Reset
### Replace with a real email from your users table
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "your-test-email@university.edu"
}

###

### 2. Reset Password with Token
### After receiving email, copy token and paste below
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "PASTE_TOKEN_FROM_EMAIL_HERE",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword123"
}

###

### 3. Login with New Password
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "your-test-email@university.edu",
  "password": "NewPassword123"
}

###

### Test: Non-existent email (should still return success for security)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "nonexistent@example.com"
}

###

### Test: Invalid token
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

